{"about_the_game":"<strong>Note:</strong> Separated is a co-op only game (2 players have to own the game to play together). It heavily relies on voice chat communication. A microphone is required and headphones are highly recommended.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Communicate!</strong></h2>You and your friend are trapped in two connected houses. There are mysterious puzzles that you have to solve together if you want to escape!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976110/extras/SolvingChinaCupboardFullWithTextIndicators.gif?t=1737433838\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Avoid the entity!</strong></h2>There's a blind entity that lurks in the shadows. It's constantly going back and forth between the houses trying to catch you. You have to avoid it at all costs!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976110/extras/AvoidPatrol2.gif?t=1737433838\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Don't let it hear you!</strong></h2>The entity might be blind but it hears EVERYTHING! Whenever you hear it, you have to be very quiet or it will come for you.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976110/extras/CaughtOnPianoTrimmed.gif?t=1737433838\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Your friend got caught!</strong></h2>The entity caught your friend a put them in a cage! You to hurry up and them out before the entity catches you too and you get stuck in the houses forever!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976110/extras/SaveYourFriendTrimmed.gif?t=1737433838\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Escape together!</strong></h2>Can you escape the clutches of the entity before it's too late?","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976110/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737433838","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstat